it.michelelacorte.swipeablecard

Class OptionView

  • java.lang.Object
    • it.michelelacorte.swipeablecard.OptionView

  • public class OptionView
extends java.lang.Object
    Option View describes the options that can be set for Swipeable Card, offers a Builder to make configuration options easier for users.
